snippet.title: Tropico 6 Trailer
snippet.description:
Prove yourself as a feared dictator or peace-loving statesman on the island state of Tropico and shape the fate of your nation through four distinctive eras. Face new challenges on the international stage and always keep the needs of your people in mind.
